                     <interp inst="t18301028-69-person640" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a constable. I went and took the prisoner - the pots have not been found.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I am innocent - I did not do it: there are five families in the house I live in, and the witness has fixed on me.</p>
